@baseUrl = {{$dotenv API_BASE_URL}}
@bookId = {{$dotenv TEST_BOOK_ID}}

### Get similar books to a specific book
GET {{baseUrl}}/recommendations/similar/{{bookId}}

### Get similar books with limit
GET {{baseUrl}}/recommendations/similar/{{bookId}}?limit=3

### Test with different book ID (replace with actual book ID from your database)
GET {{baseUrl}}/recommendations/similar/cm123book456id?limit=5
